Class LonLatPoint

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords.Coordinate
org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords.Point
org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords.LonLatPoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
@Embeddable @VoDml(id="coords:LonLatPoint", role=dataType) public class LonLatPoint extends Point implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
A spatial coordinate in a Spherical coordinate space defining a Celestial position in Latitude and Longitude. Any associated CoordSpace MUST conform to this description. If no CoordSpace is provided, a Standard Spherical CoordSpace is assumed. Values for unused/undefined dimensions need not be provided. dataType: LonLatPoint
